3. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the boat is not the egyptian##6
5. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
6. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the brazilian is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person driving the snowmobile##7
8. the person driving the scooter is not the italian##6
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |     4      |
