3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
4. the fan of d&b is between the indonesian and the owner of the rabbit##2
5. the nigerian is not the fan of r&b##6
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
7. the owner of the rabbit is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | d&b        | r&b        | rock   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian   | indonesian | french |
| Pet           | rabbit  | guinea-pig | fish       | ferret |

