3. the mexican is in an even position##4
4. the fan of metal is on the right of the turkish##1
5. the fan of punk is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
6. the mexican is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the mexican is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is sailing##7
8. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
9. the fan of blues is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is cricket##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |     4     |
