.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, soy-milk, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, egyptian, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, skateboard, tram
 1. the american is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the skateboard is between the canadian and the egyptian##2
 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the canadian is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the american is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
10. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the american is between the egyptian and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | sprite     | fanta      | milk     |
| Nationality   | turkish  | canadian   | american   | egyptian |
| Transport     | tram     | helicopter | skateboard | roller   |

