The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, funk, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, skateboarding, surfing
1. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the fan of indie##7
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the fan of electronic##7
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
4. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
5. the person eating corn is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
8. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the fan of d&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | cucumber | corn          | carrot  |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | d&b      | electronic    | indie   |
| Sport         | parkour | cycling  | skateboarding | surfing |

